  "lore": {
    "key": "Tbl_Unit_Desc_9",
    "english": "Taimanin, Gosha Academy student. Talented and experienced, she is well known as her nickname \"Demon Fists\".\n\nA classmate and a childhood friend of Akiyama Rinko, the \"Savage Hunter\". These two are known as 'the Double Rin of the Taimanin', the two most prominent Taimanin students.\n\nA master of Taimanin Art, she wields the power of Smoke Art that can turn her fists into a purple smoke. She can attack anybody within 30m of her reach. Her weapon of choice is a pair of knuckle-dusters made of rare orichalcum.",
    "japanese": "Taimanin, Gosha Academy student. Talented and experienced, she is well known as her nickname \"Demon Fists\".\n\nA classmate and a childhood friend of Akiyama Rinko, the \"Savage Hunter\". These two are known as 'the Double Rin of the Taimanin', the two most prominent Taimanin students.\n\nA master of Taimanin Art, she wields the power of Smoke Art that can turn her fists into a purple smoke. She can attack anybody within 30m of her reach. Her weapon of choice is a pair of knuckle-dusters made of rare orichalcum.",
    "korean": "Taimanin, Gosha Academy student. Talented and experienced, she is well known as her nickname \"Demon Fists\".\n\nA classmate and a childhood friend of Akiyama Rinko, the \"Savage Hunter\". These two are known as 'the Double Rin of the Taimanin', the two most prominent Taimanin students.\n\nA master of Taimanin Art, she wields the power of Smoke Art that can turn her fists into a purple smoke. She can attack anybody within 30m of her reach. Her weapon of choice is a pair of knuckle-dusters made of rare orichalcum.",
    "chinese_simplified": "Taimanin, Gosha Academy student. Talented and experienced, she is well known as her nickname \"Demon Fists\".\n\nA classmate and a childhood friend of Akiyama Rinko, the \"Savage Hunter\". These two are known as 'the Double Rin of the Taimanin', the two most prominent Taimanin students.\n\nA master of Taimanin Art, she wields the power of Smoke Art that can turn her fists into a purple smoke. She can attack anybody within 30m of her reach. Her weapon of choice is a pair of knuckle-dusters made of rare orichalcum.",
    "chinese_traditional": "Taimanin, Gosha Academy student. Talented and experienced, she is well known as her nickname \"Demon Fists\".\n\nA classmate and a childhood friend of Akiyama Rinko, the \"Savage Hunter\". These two are known as 'the Double Rin of the Taimanin', the two most prominent Taimanin students.\n\nA master of Taimanin Art, she wields the power of Smoke Art that can turn her fists into a purple smoke. She can attack anybody within 30m of her reach. Her weapon of choice is a pair of knuckle-dusters made of rare orichalcum.",
    "spanish": "Taimanin, Gosha Academy student. Talented and experienced, she is well known as her nickname \"Demon Fists\".\n\nA classmate and a childhood friend of Akiyama Rinko, the \"Savage Hunter\". These two are known as 'the Double Rin of the Taimanin', the two most prominent Taimanin students.\n\nA master of Taimanin Art, she wields the power of Smoke Art that can turn her fists into a purple smoke. She can attack anybody within 30m of her reach. Her weapon of choice is a pair of knuckle-dusters made of rare orichalcum."
